(409, 151, '_en_baseline', 'field_55511b6eb1310'),
(410, 151, 'en_content', 'A masterful knowledge of the history of the book, book binding, and book decoration from all periods, in addition to a well-chosen collection of tools, make La Feuille d''Or the perfect choice for guilding of all periods and styles.'),
